  "description": "Inspired by iChun's Hats, Titles allows player earn titles which can be displayed next to their name. This is primarily through advancements.",
  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/n7KlPYS8/images/c5c2a377d689d0db49e43a3360bd1cc05593b5d0.png\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Press 't' (you will most likely have to change this as the default chat key is also 't') to open the Titles gui. Understand that you may not have any titles to choose from at first. Simply complete advancements&nbsp; to start growing your selection.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/aurilux\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/UuQeMyv.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"268\" height=\"63\" /></a><a href=\"https://discord.gg/25E3vWdAdj\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8xVHpn6.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"268\" height=\"63\" /></a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/AuriluxDev\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nZJykla.png\" width=\"268\" height=\"63\" /></a></p>\n \n\n",
